---
import Layout from '../layouts/Layout.astro';
import NewsletterForm from '../components/NewsletterForm.astro';
---

<Layout
  title="About Jeremy Pittman | Build with Jeremy"
  description="Learn about Jeremy Pittman - entrepreneur, product builder, and former Googler helping solopreneurs and small teams streamline their businesses."
>
  <!-- Hero Section -->
  <section class="bg-white py-16 lg:py-24">
    <div class="max-w-7xl mx-auto px-4 sm:px-6 lg:px-8">
      <div class="grid grid-cols-1 lg:grid-cols-2 gap-12 items-center">
        <div>
          <h1 class="text-4xl md:text-5xl font-bold text-gray-900">
            Meet Jeremy
          </h1>
          <p class="mt-2 text-xl text-primary font-medium">
            Your Partner for Smoother, Smarter Growth
          </p>
          <div class="mt-8 text-lg text-gray-600 space-y-4">
            <p>
              I'm Jeremy Pittman — entrepreneur, product builder, and former Googler.
            </p>
            <p>
              After years building systems for global teams and growing my own businesses, I saw the same pattern everywhere: talented business owners getting stuck not because they lacked skills — but because their backend was a mess.
            </p>
            <p>
              Today, I work with solopreneurs and small businesses to fix that. My approach is real-world tested (not tech theory) and built for people who are busy, ambitious, and want their business to support their life — not take it over.
            </p>
            <p>
              Whether you're launching your first product or scaling past six figures, I help you build the operational foundation that makes growth sustainable — without burning out.
            </p>
          </div>
        </div>
        <div class="relative">
          <img
            src="/images/jeremy-head-shot.webp"
            alt="Jeremy Pittman"
            class="rounded-2xl shadow-2xl"
            loading="eager"
          />
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- Background Section -->
  <section class="bg-slate-100 py-16 lg:py-24">
    <div class="max-w-4xl mx-auto px-4 sm:px-6 lg:px-8">
      <h2 class="text-3xl md:text-4xl font-bold text-gray-900 text-center">
        My Journey
      </h2>
      <div class="mt-12 space-y-8">
        <div class="bg-white rounded-xl p-8 shadow-sm">
          <h3 class="text-xl font-bold text-primary">Former Googler</h3>
          <p class="mt-3 text-gray-600">
            I spent years at Google learning how to build systems that scale. I saw firsthand how the right processes and tools can transform how teams work — and how the wrong ones can create chaos.
          </p>
        </div>
        <div class="bg-white rounded-xl p-8 shadow-sm">
          <h3 class="text-xl font-bold text-primary">Entrepreneur & Product Builder</h3>
          <p class="mt-3 text-gray-600">
            I've built and grown multiple businesses from scratch. I know what it's like to wear every hat, work endless hours, and feel like you're constantly putting out fires. I also know how to fix it.
          </p>
        </div>
        <div class="bg-white rounded-xl p-8 shadow-sm">
          <h3 class="text-xl font-bold text-primary">Systems Obsessed</h3>
          <p class="mt-3 text-gray-600">
            I believe every business deserves smart systems — not complicated software or expensive consultants, but practical solutions that actually work for your unique situation.
          </p>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- Values Section -->
  <section class="py-16 lg:py-24">
    <div class="max-w-4xl mx-auto px-4 sm:px-6 lg:px-8">
      <h2 class="text-3xl md:text-4xl font-bold text-gray-900 text-center">
        How I Work
      </h2>
      <div class="mt-12 grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-2 gap-8">
        <div>
          <div class="h-12 w-12 bg-primary/10 rounded-lg flex items-center justify-center">
            <svg class="h-6 w-6 text-primary" fill="none" viewBox="0 0 24 24" stroke="currentColor">
              <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M9 12l2 2 4-4m6 2a9 9 0 11-18 0 9 9 0 0118 0z" />
            </svg>
          </div>
          <h3 class="mt-4 text-lg font-bold text-gray-900">Real-World Tested</h3>
          <p class="mt-2 text-gray-600">
            Everything I recommend has been tested in actual businesses — not just theory from a textbook.
          </p>
        </div>
        <div>
          <div class="h-12 w-12 bg-primary/10 rounded-lg flex items-center justify-center">
            <svg class="h-6 w-6 text-primary" fill="none" viewBox="0 0 24 24" stroke="currentColor">
              <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M13 10V3L4 14h7v7l9-11h-7z" />
            </svg>
          </div>
          <h3 class="mt-4 text-lg font-bold text-gray-900">Quick Wins First</h3>
          <p class="mt-2 text-gray-600">
            We start with the changes that give you immediate relief, then build from there.
          </p>
        </div>
        <div>
          <div class="h-12 w-12 bg-primary/10 rounded-lg flex items-center justify-center">
            <svg class="h-6 w-6 text-primary" fill="none" viewBox="0 0 24 24" stroke="currentColor">
              <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M17 20h5v-2a3 3 0 00-5.356-1.857M17 20H7m10 0v-2c0-.656-.126-1.283-.356-1.857M7 20H2v-2a3 3 0 015.356-1.857M7 20v-2c0-.656.126-1.283.356-1.857m0 0a5.002 5.002 0 019.288 0M15 7a3 3 0 11-6 0 3 3 0 016 0zm6 3a2 2 0 11-4 0 2 2 0 014 0zM7 10a2 2 0 11-4 0 2 2 0 014 0z" />
            </svg>
          </div>
          <h3 class="mt-4 text-lg font-bold text-gray-900">Partnership, Not Projects</h3>
          <p class="mt-2 text-gray-600">
            I'm not here to hand you a report and disappear. I work alongside you to make sure things actually get done.
          </p>
        </div>
        <div>
          <div class="h-12 w-12 bg-primary/10 rounded-lg flex items-center justify-center">
            <svg class="h-6 w-6 text-primary" fill="none" viewBox="0 0 24 24" stroke="currentColor">
              <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M4.318 6.318a4.5 4.5 0 000 6.364L12 20.364l7.682-7.682a4.5 4.5 0 00-6.364-6.364L12 7.636l-1.318-1.318a4.5 4.5 0 00-6.364 0z" />
            </svg>
          </div>
          <h3 class="mt-4 text-lg font-bold text-gray-900">Built for Your Life</h3>
          <p class="mt-2 text-gray-600">
            Your business should support your life goals, not consume them. Everything we build keeps that in mind.
          </p>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- CTA Section -->
  <section class="bg-slate-900 text-white py-16 lg:py-24">
    <div class="max-w-4xl mx-auto px-4 sm:px-6 lg:px-8 text-center">
      <h2 class="text-3xl md:text-4xl font-bold">
        Ready to Work Together?
      </h2>
      <p class="mt-4 text-lg text-slate-300 max-w-2xl mx-auto">
        Let's talk about where you are, where you want to go, and how I can help you get there.
      </p>
      <a href="/contact" class="mt-8 btn btn-primary text-lg px-8 py-4 inline-block">
        Book My FREE Consultation
      </a>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- Newsletter Section -->
  <section class="py-16 lg:py-24">
    <div class="max-w-4xl mx-auto px-4 sm:px-6 lg:px-8">
      <NewsletterForm
        variant="card"
        title="Stay Connected"
        description="Get tips on building smarter systems delivered to your inbox."
        buttonText="Subscribe"
      />
    </div>
  </section>
</Layout>
